&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;We are seeking an experienced Business Operations Specialist to support and drive end-&amp;nbsp;to-end sales and operational processes across the customer lifecycle. The ideal candidate&amp;nbsp;will possess strong expertise in Salesforce CRM, quoting, order processing, order booking,sales reporting, pipeline management, and cross-functional operational coordination.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;This role will work closely with Sales, Customer Success, Field Operations, Finance, andLeadership teams to ensure smooth execution from opportunity creation through&amp;nbsp;deployment, invoicing, and customer onboarding.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage end-to-end sales operations processes including opportunity management, quoting, order processing, order booking, renewals, and contract administration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support sales teams throughout the sales cycle by ensuring opportunities, quotes, and orders are accurately managed within Salesforce.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure data accuracy and compliance across Salesforce opportunities, accounts, quotes, contracts, bookings, and customer records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create, maintain, and enhance Salesforce reports, dashboards, KPI scorecards, and operational metrics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze sales pipeline performance, bookings, forecast accuracy, conversion rates, and business trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a subject matter expert on ARR, ACV, TCV, bookings, renewals, sales forecasting, and pipeline management.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with Field Operations teams to track installation schedules, deployment readiness, device availability, and implementation progress.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Customer Success Managers (CSMs) to monitor customer onboarding, deployments, implementation milestones, and operational readiness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with Sales teams to manage trial requests, trial tracking, trial conversions, commercial approvals, and customer communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Finance and Accounts teams to resolve invoicing, billing, purchase order, payment, and credit-related issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure alignment between customer contracts, deployments, installations, bookings, invoices, and Salesforce records.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive timely resolution of operational issues by coordinating across Sales, Customer Success, Field Operations, Finance, and other stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
