&lt;li&gt;Develop backend components and services for data processing systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deploy, monitor, and troubleshoot production data systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with distributed systems in containerized environments (Docker,&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Kubernetes/EKS).&lt;/li&gt;
