&lt;li&gt;Follow engineering best practices including code quality, testing, and CI/CD&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;pipelines (Jenkins).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with AI agents to solve data engineering problems at hand&lt;/li&gt;
